{"TopicId":179181,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Rocket roll","CreatedByName":"Robert Kerman","CreatedById":192487,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T04:36:03Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Robert Kerman","CreatedById":192487,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T04:36:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, so last time my rockets were \u0022dancing\u0022 at 8,000 meters, now they are rotating uncontrollably... I am literally gonna go insane and throw my computer out the window, its like trying to have a normal conversation with cleverbot evie, Its impossible!!!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T06:55:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E[snip]\u003C/span\u003E\u00A0By \u0022rotating\u0022, I\u0027m going to assume that you mean endwise. That is such a common problem for newbies that there is an entire FAQ thread in this forum called \u0022Why is my flipping rocket flipping?\u0022 It happens in general because the drag on the front end of your rocket is higher than the drag at the back end of your rocket.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-10-22T13:48:44Z\u0022 title=\u002210/22/2018 01:48  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 22, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Val\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ESnipped necromoan\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T08:05:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223472998\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002233436\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540182963\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192487\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Robert Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Robert Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, so last time my rockets were \u0022dancing\u0022 at 8,000 meters, now they are rotating uncontrollably... I am literally gonna go insane and throw my computer out the window, its like trying to have a normal conversation with cleverbot evie, Its impossible!!!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd struts, add fins.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, a rocket that looks right flies right.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T08:16:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223473045\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002233436\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540195554\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188222\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xd the great\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n47 minutes ago, Xd the great said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, a rocket that looks right flies right.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs long you keep the engines facing into the right direction! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-10-22T09:54:42Z\u0022 title=\u002210/22/2018 09:54  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 22, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Lisias\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Ebad grammars\u2026 X(\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robert Kerman","CreatedById":192487,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T09:05:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223473037\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002233436\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540191307\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154251\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022bewing\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, bewing said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBy \u0022rotating\u0022, I\u0027m going to assume that you mean endwise. That is such a common problem for newbies that there is an entire FAQ thread in this forum called \u0022Why is my flipping rocket flipping?\u0022 It happens in general because the drag on the front end of your rocket is higher than the drag at the back end of your rocket.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, thank you for your response, I know the thread old but I was stressed out and I tried to find help, ill try to properly reshape the airstream protective shell, I think I made the airstream shell a little to pointy at the end which might be the reason why.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223473045\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002233436\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540195554\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188222\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xd the great\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Xd the great said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd struts, add fins.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBasically, a rocket that looks right flies right.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTried adding struts and fins, those made it worse \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E (My rocket did not have boosters so I could not add struts but I tried anyway)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-10-22T13:49:38Z\u0022 title=\u002210/22/2018 01:49  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 22, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Val\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EUpdated quote\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Harry Rhodan","CreatedById":119953,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T09:24:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhenever you talk about a specific design: at least provide a screenshot.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T09:55:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223473059\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002233436\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540199114\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192487\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Robert Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n50 minutes ago, Robert Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, thank you for your response, I know the thread old but I was stressed out and I tried to find help, ill try to properly reshape the airstream protective shell, I think I made the airstream shell a little to pointy at the end which might be the reason why.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTried adding struts and fins, those made it worse \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E (My rocket did not have boosters so I could not add struts but I tried anyway)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you switch on \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E? Default key is T\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr use gimbal engines and moving fins. Reaction wheels, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003Ercs\u003C/abbr\u003E...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robert Kerman","CreatedById":192487,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T11:35:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223473070\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002233436\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540202154\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188222\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xd the great\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Xd the great said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you switch on \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E? Default key is T\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr use gimbal engines and moving fins. Reaction wheels, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003Ercs\u003C/abbr\u003E...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E just makes it rotate even faster, not sure what to do about it.\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Val","CreatedById":126227,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T13:52:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont color=\u0022#c0392b\u0022\u003ESplit into its\u00A0own topic and removed necromoaning.\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T14:38:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223473096\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022179181\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540208144\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192487\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Robert Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Robert Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E just makes it rotate even faster, not sure what to do about it.\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich symmetry mode did you use?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you invert any probe cores? A craft file would be nice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-22T15:32:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223472998\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022179181\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540182963\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192487\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Robert Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Robert Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, so last time my rockets were \u0022dancing\u0022 at 8,000 meters, now they are rotating uncontrollably... I am literally gonna go insane and throw my computer out the window, its like trying to have a normal conversation with cleverbot evie, Its impossible!!!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you post a screenshot of your rocket, please?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022Pointy in the front, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Center of Mass\u0022\u003ECoM\u003C/abbr\u003E near the front, fins at the back\u0022 is the standard answer.\u00A0 However, KSP provides so many different ways to build rockets that it\u0027s just about impossible for anyone to help you without \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eseeing your rocket\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(It\u0027s kind of like, suppose you had a problem with your car, so you walk into an auto repair shop \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Ewithout your car\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E and say \u0022My car doesn\u0027t work, what should I do?\u0022\u00A0 Well, the first thing the mechanics are going to want to do is to \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Etake a look at the car\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E.)\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are some very simple design principles in KSP that will make it very easy to design rockets that don\u0027t flip-- but even though they\u0027re \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Esimple\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E, they\u0027re not \u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003Eobvious\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E if you\u0027re new to the game and don\u0027t know what they are.\u00A0 Chances are high that there\u0027s something very simple about your rocket, that will be obvious at a glance for an experienced player.\u00A0 So, if you can just post a picture of your rocket, it\u0027s fairly likely that we can give you specific and helpful advice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robert Kerman","CreatedById":192487,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-28T14:10:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh! Looks like somehow my rockets heat shield had something to do with the rotation, so I rebuilt my rocket and now its fine. (It was a custom version of the Apollo 12)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-28T15:47:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223476860\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022179181\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540735843\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022192487\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Robert Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Robert Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh! Looks like somehow my rockets heat shield had something to do with the rotation, so I rebuilt my rocket and now its fine. (It was a custom version of the Apollo 12)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you sure it wasn\u0027t just struck by lightning?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Robert Kerman","CreatedById":192487,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-29T01:31:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223476896\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022179181\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221540741672\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you sure it wasn\u0027t just struck by lightning?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWish there was a mod for weather in ksp... I mean I got the grannus expansion pack, and yes the weather was clear when i launched my rocket, soo.... no lightning.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}